D_8
V=\langle x,y\mid x^2=y^2=1, xy=yx \rangle
C_2=\langle a \mid a^2=1 \rangle
x=\begin{pmatrix}1\\0\end{pmatrix}
y=\begin{pmatrix}0\\1\end{pmatrix}
\phi_a(y)
D_8=V\rtimes_\phi C_2, \; \text{where} \; \phi(a)=\begin{pmatrix}1&1\\0&1\end{pmatrix}
\phi_a(x)=\begin{pmatrix}1&1\\0&1\end{pmatrix}\begin{pmatrix}1\\0\end{pmatrix}=\begin{pmatrix}1\\0\end{pmatrix}=x
\phi_a(y)=\begin{pmatrix}1&1\\0&1\end{pmatrix}\begin{pmatrix}0\\1\end{pmatrix}=\begin{pmatrix}1\\1\end{pmatrix}
